                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">City-policeman,</hi> 444). The prisoner was given into my custody on the morning of 24th February—I got this broken half-crown (<hi rend="italic">produced</hi>) from the last witness—when the prisoner was searched, there was found on him 4<hi rend="italic">s</hi>. 4<hi rend="italic">d</hi>. in coppers, and a bad shilling—he said he had no home in London.</p>
